<p> A preview of DECOLONIZING MENTAL HEALTH, an original digital series 
that dismantles the racism underscoring the mental healthcare industry. 
By focusing its gaze on the transformative work of therapists and 
individuals of color, it calls for redressal of the ways in which we 
define psychiatric illness and health. </p>
